{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HMAC（密钥散列消息认证码）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HMAC","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HMAC（密钥散列消息认证码）是一个被用于<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">密码学 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的认证消息协议。它可以使用于任何的<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptographic_hash_function\">密码学函数 <small>(en-US)</small></a>。它的强度依赖底层的函数（例如 SHA1 或 MD5）以及被选中的密钥。出于这样使用上的组合，HMAC 认证<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Algorithm\">算法</a>通常是以组合名字出现，如 HMAC-SHA1。</p>\n<p>HMAC 通常用于确保完整性和身份验证。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基础知识","title":"基础知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E6%95%A3%E5%88%97%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HMAC</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>IETF 的 <a href=\"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2104.txt\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 2104</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"HMAC（密钥散列消息认证码）是一个被用于密码学 (en-US)的认证消息协议。它可以使用于任何的密码学函数 (en-US)。它的强度依赖底层的函数（例如 SHA1 或 MD5）以及被选中的密钥。出于这样使用上的组合，HMAC 认证算法通常是以组合名字出现，如 HMAC-SHA1。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HMAC","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HMAC","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HMAC","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/hmac","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/hmac/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a